<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="merely-adv">merely <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'mɪəli/    美 /'mɪrli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-only-simply">1.★ <strong>仅仅；只不过 (only / simply)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I asked it merely out of curiosity. 
我只不过出于好奇问问而已。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is <strong>not merely</strong> a job, but a way of life.
这不仅仅是一份工作，而是一种生活方式。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>I wasn’t blaming anyone; I <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (mere) said errors like this could be avoided.  （2010 湖北改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. merely  </p></div>